TROUGHS LYING ACROSS NERN BRITAIN AND AN ASSOCIATED ELONGATED LOW NEAR 987
LYING TO THE NW OF THE BRITISH ISLES. AT THE SAME TIME A DEEPER LOW IS LIKELY
